configparam.description: Configuration parameter containing information on the location and parsing of csv files used by the client uploader process. HDB - name of hdb process data is to be added to tab - table name for upload of data partedCol - name of column for data to be sorted on whereClause - way to filter data to be written to disk updateCols - used to update/add cols to raw data from csv file dateParted - true if table is date partitioned separator - file delimiter (e.g. , for csv file)
